st, Yup, Searchcaster, Launchcaster, Eventcaster, and Casthose. Each takes =
a different twist to the frontend experience of accessing Farcaster=E2=80=
=99s data and interacting with its users.=C2=A0
A few months ago, the Farcaster team introduced channels as a way to organi=
ze conversations by topic. The Farcaster team created the first few channel=
