7b0-c8ad-4660-a274-41002e7abc63?j=3DeyJ1IjoiOXAwZ3QifQ.gb8J5T7GnA_ZlNuaMZjm=
lXXepKbqOsa8-6m8ExkRNpU ].=C2=A0=C2=A0
And it=E2=80=99s good for Farcaster, because it means that thousands of dev=
elopers and creators will be working to build experiences that attract acti=
vities and users, and that the Farcaster protocol has a shot at becoming th=
