networks like Facebook and Twitter and protocols networks like SMTP and HTT=
P. &#8220;Blockchains are the only credible, known architecture,&#8221; he =
writes, &#8220;for building networks with the societal benefits of protocol=
 networks and the competitive advantages of corporate networks.&#8221; Farc=
aster is a blockchain network.</span></p><p style=3D"color: rgb(64, 64, 64)=
; font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; margin: 0 0 20px 0;">The benefits of =
blockchain networks can be hard to grok in the abstract. What&#8217;s happe=
